    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"stop fighting the current and let yourself be held by the water\" ... what does that even mean? it sounds like you're saying i should just give up. like there's nothing left for me to do but just let it happen. because honestly, looking at the numbers and the legal stuff, it feels like the math just doesn't work out. there's no way I'm ever getting my life back.",
