    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like a trap. no matter what i do, the hole just gets deeper. it's like i'm just a burden to everyone, and the only way to actually end this cycle of debt and misery is to just... not be here anymore. is it even wrong to want the pain to just stop for good?",
